chore: optimize check for modifications in git repository

Why:
- The existing code for checking modifications in the git repository needed optimization.

Changes:
- Updated the function to exclude certain directories ('.gitdisable/' and 'migrations/') from the check for modifications.
- Printed a clearer output of the modifications found in the repository.
- Added a check to return True if there are more than one modified files.

